#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/transform/transform_control/pivot_point/individual_origins.rst:57
msgid ""
"In Edit Mode, setting the Pivot Point to Individual Origins produces "
"different results when the selection mode is set to Vertex, Edge or Face."
" For example, Vertex mode produces results similar to setting the pivot "
"point to median and Edge mode often produces distorted results. Using "
"Individual Origins in Face mode produces the most predictable results."
msgstr ""

